name: Vanessa Cloke
biography: Originally Vanessa Dimitropoulos. She has been acting and dancing since childhood, but did not pursue acting as a career until 2007 after living in Spain for 3 years. Since then, she has worked on several TV shows and features including American Horror Story, The Big Short, and Treme. She holds a Bachelors in Communications from Chapman University. Acting professionally is truly a dream come true.::Vanessa Cloke
